I am convinced that every person's long-term happiness depends crucially on self-empowerment and community support. 

Helping people to redress inequality through improvements in local business and local infrastructure is an important part of a sustainably happy future for all. I see Kiva loans as a way to get us there effectively.
lenders.occupational_info:
Free software is any digital information (and especially computer programs) which all recipients are legally free to improve and share, to help themselves and each other.

My work with organisations and individuals is ordinary in that I achieve business and organisation goals with computers. What makes it interesting for me is that all the solutions I work on use free software, so the recipients are free from anyone trying to restrict what they do with it.

I get a lot of satisfaction from knowing that my customers will not beg for continued service, but choose to continue paying for my help with their ongoing goals.
